@startuml
' --- whole-map provenance: cycle that introduced each @id ---
' @cycle(CMP-MAP-SCOPE-ENGINE, 0030)
' @cycle(CMP-MAP-SCOPE-CLI, 0030)
' @id(CMP-MAP-SCOPE-ENGINE)
' @desc(CMP-MAP-SCOPE-ENGINE, "Project::map_scope(cycle_number, base) -> MapScopePlan in crates/mdd-core/src/lib.rs. Reads model_registry (current @id -> diagram file), read_trace (source_links), and cycle_registry().cycle(N).manifest (scope). REVERSE: traceability::changed_code(root, base) -> changed source files; for each, source_links filtered by path -> model_ids -> current diagram files into a BTreeSet; a changed file with no matching source_link -> scope_escape. FORWARD: each manifest scope @id -> current concept file (mirror current path when not yet on current side). full_remap = !scope_escapes.is_empty(). Pure/read-only; reuses the existing changed_code engine — no new git/syn machinery. Unit-tested (map_scope_narrows_to_diagrams_linked_to_changed_source, map_scope_unlinked_change_forces_full_remap).")
' @id(CMP-MAP-SCOPE-CLI)
' @desc(CMP-MAP-SCOPE-CLI, "Commands::MapScope { cycle, base (default HEAD), json } in crates/mdd-cli/src/main.rs -> Project::map_scope(cycle, &base). --json prints MapScopePlan; text mode prints full-remap escapes, the empty case, or the affected diagram list. Always exits 0 (a plan, not a gate).")
title MDD scoped re-map — ownership (current)

actor "Developer / Agent" as Dev

component "mdd map-scope\n(CMP-MAP-SCOPE-CLI)" as Cli
component "Project::map_scope\n(CMP-MAP-SCOPE-ENGINE)" as Engine
component "CycleRegistry\n(CMP-CORE-CYCLE-MODEL)" as CycleModel
component "trace.yml source_links" as Trace
component "changed_code\n(CMP-TRACE-ENGINE)" as TraceEngine
component "/mdd-map skill\n(CMP-MAP-SKILL)" as MapSkill
component "/mdd-cycle skill\n(CMP-CYCLE-ORCHESTRATOR)" as Cycle

Dev --> Cli : mdd map-scope --cycle N [--base REF] [--json]
Cli --> Engine : map_scope(N, base)
Engine --> CycleModel : cycle(N).manifest.scope
Engine --> Trace : source_links by path
Engine --> TraceEngine : changed_code(root, base)
Cycle --> Cli : each loop iteration
Cycle --> MapSkill : pass affected_files / full_remap

note bottom of Engine
  Reuses traceability::changed_code (Rust/src diff).
  full_remap forces a whole-tree re-map. Realized by SEQ-MAP-SCOPE.
end note
@enduml
